text: Dimitar Yordanov (born 4 February 1928) is a Bulgarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Bulgarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
